metadata.title: QUIPU-DECODE + Σ-Kernel Analysis: CORNELL_AS10_SIGMA
metadata.author: Dr. Guilherme de Camargo
metadata.abstract: Comprehensive analysis of CORNELL_AS10_SIGMA using QUIPU-DECODE Framework v1.0 with Σ-Kernel deductive reasoning. Results demonstrate cognitive scaffolding function and information encoding capabilities.

cognitive_analysis.interpretation: High working memory load suggests quipu functions as cognitive scaffolding; High information density indicates efficient encoding system
